vote.title: Authorize (1) the adoption of a Resolution of Support for Generation Housing Partners, LLC and/or its affiliate(s) (Applicant), related to its application to the Texas Department of Housing and Community Affairs (TDHCA) for 9% Housing Tax Credits for the development The Heights at Park Lane to be located at 9310 North Central Expressway, Dallas, Texas 75231; and (2) an agreement with the Applicant for a line of credit in the amount of $500.00 for the proposed multifamily development - Not to exceed $500.00 - Financing: General Fund
